{"tid":1876370,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"物流署訂逾5300萬個口罩    僅400萬個抵港","createTime":"2020-02-12T10:54:14.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-12T11:47:14.000Z","uid":79563,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"c59b35b0eff98e83277b04df892ffd208ff780cf","tid":1876370,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-12T10:54:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/_TMui6as6Jptm9aPBbJ8qQ--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9ODAw/https://media.zenfs.com/ko/onccinstantnews.com/5fa03d7dfa8ca84d679b82df3cc69b95\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2F_TMui6as6Jptm9aPBbJ8qQ--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9ODAw%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fko%2Fonccinstantnews.com%2F5fa03d7dfa8ca84d679b82df3cc69b95&h=3723bb43&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n肺炎疫情爆發後，市民急忙購買口罩防疫，各大藥房口罩嚴重短缺。物流署今日(12日)亦指，目前已訂購逾5300萬個口罩，當中400萬個已運抵香港，僅得訂購量的7.5%。<br />\n<br />\n現時市面「一罩難求」，政府在全球訂購逾5300萬個口罩，惟只有少數運抵本港，此批口罩會首先供應予醫護人員及需接觸病者的人員，內部有守則說明，主要向在工作上需要與市民頻繁接觸、在人多地方工作、工作有需要，又或身體有狀況的人員分派口罩。截至周日(9日)，政府口罩庫存僅得1200萬個，預計只夠應付1個月用量。"},{"pid":"9a91d64885b257273d658836a91e4b34c539c7be","tid":1876370,"uid":214502,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-12T11:15:32.000Z","msg":"價低者得 邊撚個賣比你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d56b31cc46ff9a39ca5194e0d86ec1e78df8fdd0","tid":1876370,"uid":60924,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"9a91d64885b257273d658836a91e4b34c539c7be","tid":1876370,"uid":214502,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-12T11:15:32.000Z","msg":"價低者得 邊撚個賣比你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-12T11:26:59.000Z","msg":"薄到透光果d<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/